Additionally, the paper discusses strategies for interpreting and visualizing the compositionality of neural models, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions using similar techniques from computer vision, which suggests that it may belong to the sub-category of Computer Vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses the performance of different types of neural networks, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
